Happy birthday mumma❤️🌎

Thank you for inspiring me each day #guru

Eversince i started seeing you, i saw you working
from every side like from home to the salon, salon
to home.I still remember how u have workd at the
salon and came home tired with no stress but with
only charming smile.
Not just the birth but you have gave mee so much
than i have askd for, not only to mee but to whom
so ever it was, it is or it will be.
I found you
beautiful, strong, intelligent, independent, Thats
It, what i have askd more with god, as he has given
everything in you, Thats how before praying to
God, i dedicately believe to pray to you.
Ur more than God To mee.Infact your My God.!!
Love you My Mimmi,Thank you for everything.!!❤️

Every bride have different
charm in her eyes, and thats make her different and
special….!!❤️
